528
00:37:09,393 --> 00:37:11,187
-It'd be nice if we could pay it back.
-What?

529
00:37:11,979 --> 00:37:14,607
-I should tell people at work, right?
-Why?

530
00:37:16,317 --> 00:37:18,569
